}}    '''Firefox Lockwise'''是[[Firefox瀏覽器|Firefox瀏覽器]]以及[[IOS|IOS]]和{{link-en|Android}}上的密码管理器。<ref>{{Cite web|title=How to Manage Web Passwords With Firefox Lockwise|url=https://www.pcmag.com/feature/367772/how-to-manage-web-passwords-with-firefox-lockwise|accessdate=2019-11-18|author=Whitney|first=By Lance|work=PCMAG|archive-date=2019-11-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191128004157/https://www.pcmag.com/feature/367772/how-to-manage-web-passwords-with-firefox-lockwise|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=Mozilla launches new desktop password manager, Firefox Lockwise|url=https://www.techradar.com/uk/news/mozilla-launches-new-desktop-password-manager-firefox-lockwise|accessdate=2019-11-18|author=Software|first=Catherine Ellis 2019-06-04T13:00:01Z|work=TechRadar|archive-date=2019-12-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191201135545/https://www.techradar.com/uk/news/mozilla-launches-new-desktop-password-manager-firefox-lockwise|dead-url=no}}</ref> 在台式机上，Lockwise只是Firefox瀏覽器的一部分<ref name="FF70">{{Cite web|title=Firefox 70.0 release notes|url=https://www.mozilla.org/firefox/70.0/releasenotes/|date=October 22, 2019|work=Mozilla}}</ref>，而在iOS和Android上，它可以作为独立应用程序使用。

如果用戶激活了[[Firefox_Sync|Firefox Sync]]，则Lockwise会在不同设备上的[[Firefox瀏覽器|Firefox瀏覽器]]之間同步密码。它还内置{{en-link|随机密码生成器|Random password generator}}。

2021年12月31日，因Lockwise功能已整合入Firefox App for Android/iOS，Firefox宣布Lockwise終止支援。<ref>{{cite web |title=End of support for Firefox Lockwise |url=https://support.mozilla.org/en-US/kb/end-of-support-firefox-lockwise |accessdate=2022-01-05 |archive-date=2022-03-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220325064001/https://support.mozilla.org/en-US/kb/end-of-support-firefox-lockwise }}</ref>

== 历史 ==
Firefox Lockwise由[[Mozilla公司|Mozilla]]开发，在2018年，當時Lockwise名为Firefox Lockbox。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Firefox Lockwise Aims to Revamp Browser Password Management|url=https://www.bleepingcomputer.com/news/security/firefox-lockwise-aims-to-revamp-browser-password-management/|accessdate=2019-11-18|work=BleepingComputer|archive-date=2019-05-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190528184957/https://www.bleepingcomputer.com/news/security/firefox-lockwise-aims-to-revamp-browser-password-management/|dead-url=no}}</ref>它在2019年5月更名为“ Lockwise”。<ref>{{Cite web|title=New Privacy Features for Mozilla Firefox, Lockwise Is Live|url=https://www.bleepingcomputer.com/news/security/new-privacy-features-for-mozilla-firefox-lockwise-is-live/|accessdate=2019-11-18|work=BleepingComputer|archive-date=2019-08-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190806011922/https://www.bleepingcomputer.com/news/security/new-privacy-features-for-mozilla-firefox-lockwise-is-live/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=Rename "Firefox Lockbox" to "Firefox Lockwise" after May 28|url=https://github.com/mozilla/bedrock/issues/7242|date=25 May 2019|work=GitHub|quote=Lockbox is getting a new name on 28 May [for the "Trailhead" release, a product update.]|access-date=2020-09-10|archive-date=2021-10-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211008132633/https://github.com/mozilla/bedrock/issues/7242}}</ref>它于2018年7月10日開始在iOS上推出。<ref name="Lockbox">{{Cite web|title=Introducing Firefox's First Mobile Test Pilot Experiments: Lockbox and Notes|url=https://blog.mozilla.org/blog/2018/07/10/introducing-firefoxs-first-mobile-test-pilot-experiments-lockbox-and-notes|accessdate=2019-06-26|author=Nguyen|first=Nick|work=The Mozilla Blog|language=en-US|archive-date=2019-09-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190904045417/https://blog.mozilla.org/blog/2018/07/10/introducing-firefoxs-first-mobile-test-pilot-experiments-lockbox-and-notes/|dead-url=no}}</ref>2019年3月26日，Lockwise的Android版本發佈。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Firefox Lockbox Now on Android, Keeping your Passwords Safe|url=https://blog.mozilla.org/blog/2019/03/26/firefox-lockbox-now-on-android-keeping-your-passwords-safe|accessdate=2019-06-26|author=Nguyen|first=Nick|work=The Mozilla Blog|language=en-US|archive-date=2019-12-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191210071302/https://blog.mozilla.org/blog/2019/03/26/firefox-lockbox-now-on-android-keeping-your-passwords-safe/|dead-url=no}}</ref> 

在台式机上，Lockwise最初是作为Firefox瀏覽器的插件而存在。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Firefox Lockbox for Desktop|url=https://github.com/mozilla-lockwise/lockwise-addon/releases|date=10 Aug 2019|publisher=Firefox|access-date=2020-09-10|archive-date=2021-12-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211201050301/https://github.com/mozilla-lockwise/lockwise-addon/releases}} (Firefox addon repository)</ref>从Firefox 70开始，Lockwise已集成到Firefox瀏覽器<ref>{{Cite web|title=Minigame: Celebrate Firefox 70's release by finding a website with 70+ trackers blocked|url=https://www.theregister.co.uk/2019/10/22/firefox_70/|accessdate=2019-11-18|author=at 19:00|first=Richard Speed 22 Oct 2019|work=www.theregister.co.uk|archive-date=2019-12-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191210070249/https://www.theregister.co.uk/2019/10/22/firefox_70/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="FF70">{{Cite web|title=Firefox 70.0 release notes|url=https://www.mozilla.org/firefox/70.0/releasenotes/|date=October 22, 2019|work=Mozilla}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=Password Manager in Firefox|url=https://support.mozilla.org/kb/password-manager-remember-delete-edit-logins?redirectlocale=en-US&redirectslug=password-manager-remember-delete-change-and-import|accessdate=26 October 2019|work=Firefox Help|quote=Password Manager is now Firefox Lockwise! The interface for managing usernames and passwords was entirely redesigned and is now based on the Firefox Lockwise add-on.}}</ref>。  

